<taxonomicName genus="Clusiaceae" lsidName="" pageId="37" pageNumber="132" rank="genus">Clusiaceae</taxonomicName>
), and observed feeding, mating and oviposition on 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Clusiaceae" genus="Hypericum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Guttiferales" pageId="37" pageNumber="132" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="punctatum">
